rifleman
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a tiny New Zealand bush bird, <i>Acanthisitta chloris</i>, [probably from green and bronze plumage resembling an early military uniform]
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See: also thumb bird
